    },
    {
      "id": "section-1",
      "title": "Base Design's Strategic Visual Identity Overhaul",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "id": "para-1-0",
          "content": "Base Design crafted the rebrand through on-site interviews and focus groups, developing a modernized wordmark blending serif and sans-serif elements to bridge past and present. The **'H' monogram** evokes institutional gravity with contemporary confidence, using a signature green palette and dynamic typographic motion to unify collections. President Karen R. Lawrence noted it demonstrates connections among library, art, and botanical elements while expanding access digitally and in-person.",
          "citations": [
            {
              "primarySource": {
                "id": "source-6",
                "name": "basedesign",
                "url": "https://www.basedesign.com/work/the-huntington",
                "favicon": "https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=www.basedesign.com&sz=32",
                "title": "The Huntington by Base Design"
              },
              "additionalCount": 1,
              "additionalSources": [
                {
                  "id": "source-7",
                  "name": "southpasadenan",
                  "url": "https://southpasadenan.com/the-huntington-launches-bold-rebrand-and-digital-initiatives-to-enhance-visitor-experience/",
                  "favicon": "https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=southpasadenan.com&sz=32",
                  "title": "The Huntington by Base Design"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "para-1-1",
          "content": "The rollout includes new signage, a refreshed website, and merchandise, with activities like immersive light shows and Sam Francis-inspired photo backdrops from April 2025. This evolution honors tradition without clichés, providing tools to articulate The Huntington's \"360° nature where nature and knowledge meet.\" It supports the institution's 12 million rare items and 175 annual fellows under \"One Huntington.\"",
          "citations": [
            {
              "primarySource": {
                "id": "source-3",
                "name": "huntington",
                "url": "https://www.huntington.org/news/huntington-revitalize-historic-library-building-and-transform-library-and-art-museum",
                "favicon": "https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=www.huntington.org&sz=32",
                "title": "The Huntington by Base Design"
              },
              "additionalCount": 1,
              "additionalSources": [
